description: I am Chef Joel St. John, owner and Chef of St. John's Fire, the brand-new, full-service gourmet food truck. You have the opportunity to bring to your office, warehouse, or parking lot a gourmet mobile food experience for your employees, customers or guests.  To take advantage of seasonal ingredients, menu will change occasionally.  I guarantee high-quality food served quickly at a reasonable price.
name: St. John's Fire
